text: Melodee and I were just talking about how helpful it would be to have a site map of screen by screen flows through the entire app so we're able to clearly identify how Sara will navigate Compass. A few of us have gotten confused numerous times trying to navigate all the wire frames in the mix. Not sure if this is something already being worked on or if it's even feasible to create but wanted to throw it out there to gauge what the UX team is thinking about this.
